        Read Error Completely and make sure its not a proxy error
    https://github.com/lthiery/SPI-Py
    https://learn.adafruit.com/series/learn-raspberry-pi
    https://www.raspberrypi.org/documentation/hardware/raspberrypi/spi/README.md
    https://www.raspberrypi.org/forums/viewtopic.php?t=106313 
        Note : Add "dtoverlay=spi-bcm2835" line to "/boot/config.txt"
        Explanation given here : https://github.com/raspberrypi/firmware/tree/master/boot/overlays
